Package: AlternativeDrugResponseMetrics
Title: Calculate and explore the usefulness of alternative drug response metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Vigneshwari", "Subramanian", email = "vignesh.bioinfo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Attila", "Gabor", email = "gabor.attila87@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: This is a package meant for calculating alternative drug response metrics such as GR, NDR and PI. Additionally, it lets you to do some exploratory analysis to find out the performances of different response metrics in terms of reproducibility, ANOVA and drug response predictions.     
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
